-empty="false">Como ganhar espa\'e7o e concorrer com grandes incorporadoras mesmo com poucos anos de hist\'f3ria pr\'f3pria?</h1><div class="flex flex-col gap-[16px] text-[16px] text-[color:var(--f53a5a83-1585-4ee8-9cad-d1da78881835)] opacity-[60%]" data-layer-id="lyr-mo4kqpx2yu5kyz" data-layer-type="div" data-is-empty="false"><p class="mt-[-8px] font-[400] max-md:text-[14px]">A Trifold possu\'eda experi\'eancia, hist\'f3rico de obras relevantes e know-how t\'e9cnico consolidado. O problema n\'e3o estava na entrega, mas na percep\'e7\'e3o.</p><p class="mt-[-8px] font-[400] max-md:text-[14px]">A marca n\'e3o comunicava com clareza seu n\'edvel de atua\'e7\'e3o, seu repert\'f3rio t\'e9cnico nem o novo momento da empresa como incorporadora. Isso gerava desalinhamento entre valor real e valor percebido.</p></div><hr class="border-t-[1px] border-[#ffffff]/10" data-layer-id="lyr-mo4l0lvpyzra7d" data-layer-type="hr" data-is-empty="true"/><div class="flex gap-[36px] max-md:flex max-md:flex-col" data-layer-id="lyr-mo4l10rkicpuv4" data-layer-type="div" data-is-empty="false"><div class="flex flex-col gap-[4px]" data-layer-id="lyr-mo4l3e2tx9aen3" data-layer-type="div" data-is-empty="false"><p class="text-[16px] font-[STIX_Two_Text_Italic] text-[#ffffff]/40" data-layer-id="lyr-mo4l3e2tcdjhro" data-layer-type="p" data-is-empty="false">Segmento</p><p class="text-[16px] text-[#ffffff]" data-layer-id="lyr-mo4l3e2tuk2lvd" data-layer-type="p" data-is-empty="false"> <!-- -->Alto Padr\'e3o</p></div><div class="flex flex-col gap-[4px]" data-layer-id="lyr-mo4lcxoxwg66kd" data-layer-type="div" data-is-empty="false"><p class="text-[16px] font-[STIX_Two_Text_Italic] text-[#ffffff]/40" data-layer-id="lyr-mo4ld6q4ii4s7x" data-layer-type="p" data-is-empty="false">Servi\'e7os</p><div class="flex flex-row gap-[0px] max-md:flex-nowrap" data-layer-id="lyr-mo4l4beqeg312t" data-layer-type="div" data-is-empty="false"></div></div></div></div></div><div class="flex flex-col absolute left-[0px] top-[0px] right-[0px] bottom-[0px] bg-[#000000]/60" data-layer-id="lyr-mo4o32pmsud5wv" data-layer-type="div" data-is-empty="true"></div></section><section class="h-auto flex flex-col overflow-hidden h-[auto] pl-[5%] pr-[5%] pt-[90px] gap-[90px] pb-[24px]" data-layer-id="lyr-mo4lhylrd43q2s" data-layer-type="section" data-is-empty="false"><div class="mr-auto ml-auto w-full flex flex-col w-[100%] max-w-[1280px] mr-[auto] ml-[auto] pr-[32px] pl-[32px] max-md:pl-[0px] max-md:pr-[0px]" data-layer-id="lyr-mo4lhylrtj55dv" data-layer-type="div" data-is-empty="false"><div class="grid max-md:grid-cols-1 max-lg:grid-cols-2 mt-[0px] grid-cols-[repeat(2,_1fr)] gap-[90px]" data-layer-id="lyr-mo4lhylr7uqc6f" data-layer-type="div" data-is-empty="false"><div class="flex items-start flex-col gap-[24px] h-Taxadeconvers\'e3onasvisitasaodecorado h-Taxadeconvers\'e3onasvisitasaodecorado w-[100%]" data-layer-id="lyr-mo4lhylrhbv679" data-layer-type="div" data-is-empty="false"><div class="flex flex-col gap-[12px]" data-layer-id="lyr-mo4lhylrsfd9hd" data-layer-type="div" data-is-empty="false"><h2 class="leading-[1.1] tracking-[-0.01em] font-[STIX_Two_Text_Italic] font-[400] text-[24px] text-[#171717]" data-layer-id="lyr-mo4mki39ywalel" data-layer-type="h2" data-is-empty="false">Desafio</h2><div class="flex flex-col gap-[16px] text-[16px]" data-layer-id="lyr-mo4sg5srn580p0" data-layer-type="div" data-is-empty="false"><p class="text-[#000000] text-[16px] opacity-[60%] max-md:text-[14px]">Al\'e9m do reposicionamento da marca, e olhando para o mercado da incorpora\'e7\'e3o a empresa precisava corrigir decis\'f5es estrat\'e9gicas anteriores, incluindo o lan\'e7amento de um produto desalinhado a estrat\'e9gia correta, o que afetou as vendas.</p></div></div></div><div class="flex items-start flex-col gap-[24px] h-Taxadeconvers\'e3onasvisitasaodecorado h-Taxadeconvers\'e3onasvisitasaodecorado" data-layer-id="lyr-mo4mn5soevpo99" data-layer-type="div" data-is-empty="false"><div class="flex flex-col gap-[12px]" 